To genarate the single training file from the directory of training files for either SPAM or SENTIMENT
1.Place the sstrain.py in that directory
2.Set the path in the terminal to that directory
3.run using the command:  python3 sstrain.py

A file with name TRAININGFILE is generated which is the file used in generating the model file by nblearn.py


To genarate the single test file from the directory of training files for either SPAM or SENTIMENT
1.Place the sstrain.py in that directory
2.Set the path in the terminal to that directory
3.run using the command:  python3 sstest.py

A file with name TESTFILE is generated which is used by nbclassify.py along with model file for classification

